{"tid":794082,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雷莊𠒇卸任在即：好開心！","createTime":"2018-08-26T02:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T01:39:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c4522fe863cab678b7f74034428d2c4a9db885d6","tid":794082,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T02:21:34.000Z","msg":"2017年港姐冠軍雷莊𠒇今晚卸任，身材向來澎湃的她昨日谷胸上陣，為S楊帆試戴后冠，搶盡師妹鏡！她笑說：「多謝！第一次見啲師妹，冇乜印象，因為之前冇跟開，最重要係聽日放多啲心機，表演時多啲自信。（卸任在即，心情如何？）好開心，一年來學咗好多嘢，會將呢啲經驗帶番去加拿大好好發展。（會唔會唔捨得到喊？）唔會，好好玩，最唔捨得係幫手化妝整頭啲幕後同事，好期待可以見番亞軍何依婷同季軍黃瑋琦，到時大家着到靚一靚出場，攞番上年嘅回憶！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mzyyTasjW7xZKyZPTPlcTg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/318092d0ba09d27bb79687806699d0bf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmzyyTasjW7xZKyZPTPlcTg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F318092d0ba09d27bb79687806699d0bf&h=e1f51e89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46386b5eba8b230136093eeb79679b6341a9f0aa","tid":794082,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T02:23:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a52f00f3144ab45b2cf1b33829a49a81e65c3dcc","tid":794082,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T02:23:46.000Z","msg":"平到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c60c6ab8690f0d97ab75f45d621d7630755345","tid":794082,"uid":23087,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T02:30:22.000Z","msg":"兩個都ipad"},{"pid":"49099ea0355846e3900287c2afc36256072f4cea","tid":794082,"uid":72688,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T02:31:03.000Z","msg":"雷莊兜好樣衰"},{"pid":"76cb2f72fde72ef8fbc5cde818314ccff366847c","tid":794082,"uid":130678,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T02:35:55.000Z"